snippet.title: My Forged Wedding Nintendo Switch™- Promotional Reel
snippet.description:
The opening movie for the Nintendo Switch™ download-only games
""My Forged Wedding""

◆Official Site◆
https://products.voltage.co.jp/switch/english/

◆Story◆
